            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;As an aside, capturing output into a variable just so you can then &lt;code&gt;echo&lt;/code&gt; the variable is a &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.iki.fi/era/unix/award.html#echo&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;useless use of &lt;code&gt;echo&lt;/code&gt;,&lt;/a&gt; and a useless use of variables.&lt;/span&gt;

